# vue-doctor Project Core

Read `AGENTS.md` for full rules. Key constraints:

- pnpm monorepo: packages/core, packages/rules, packages/cli
- All detection is deterministic AST — no LLM, no regex on source code
- MVP scope: CLI + rules + score + JSON + GitHub Action only
- Public surface changes require product-thinking skill first
- New rules: tests first, then implementation (vue-doctor-rule-writing skill)

When implementing, always check `docs/02-feature-plan.md` for feature ID and acceptance criteria.
